review:
My Father had met with an accident. When we contacted doctor after taking an x-ray. He was very quick to pick up the call and response us. And gave us the confidence to travel all the way from Chennai to bangalore and came on Sunday to visit and made all the arrangements and did the test on Sunday and on Monday morning the Surgery happened. Dr. A. K Jeelani and Dr. Ahmed were very helpful and did everything with ease.

And my father was very much happy we came here and met the correct doctor.
reply_text:
A pleasant surprise that you drove down all the way from Chennai to fix your broken knee here with us. Glad that Surgery went on well and as promised we made your father to start walking from the very next day. 

Patients like you who put their 100% faith and trust in doctors always get best results.
